title: Championne - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Championne performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 06, 2023. 

Songs:
Rien
Fête
Petite mort

Mathilde LEJAS - Vocals, Guitar
Louis Kuipers - Guitar, Vocals
Blanche LEBLOND - Bass, Vocals
Florian Pardigon - Drums, Vocals
Nice - Keyboards, Vocals

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer:
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
